<inglise> Whereas the aim of Directive 93/88/EEC establishing a first list of biological agents on the basis of the definitions given in Article 2 point (d) numbers 2, 3 and 4 of Directive 90/679/EEC is to harmonize conditions in this field while maintaining the progress made; </inglise>
